-- Gold Must Be Held in Current Economic Environment, Pento Says
-- B y   J o h n   D e a n e
-- 2012-03-13T13:43:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/gold-must-be-held-in-current-economic-environment-pento-says.html
Gold must be held in an environment
in which the  Federal Reserve  has pledged to maintain low
 interest rates  and the U.S government is running current-level
deficits,  Michael Pento , president, Pento Portfolio Strategies,
said at the Bloomberg Precious Metals conference in  New York .  “We have to own gold,” in this environment, Pento said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 John Deane  in London at 
